<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.9.4">
<l>māṟṟuttāy ceṉṟu vaṉampōkē yeṉṟiṭa</l>
<l>vīṟṟuttāy piṉtoṭarn tempirā ṉeṉṟaḻa</l>
<l>kūṟṟuttāy collak koṭiyava ṉampōṉa</l>
<l>cīṟṟa milātāṉaip pāṭippaṟa</l>
<l rend="indent">cītai maṇāḷaṉaip pāṭippaṟa</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Jump and sing about him who is without anger, who,</l>
<l rend="indent">when [his] step-mother approached</l>
<l rend="indent">[him and] said “go to the forest!</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] his own mother followed after</l>
<l rend="indent">[him] weeping, “our Lord!”</l>
<l>went to the cruel forest</l>
<l rend="indent">when the mother of death commanded [it].</l>
<l>Jump and sing about the bridegroom of Sītā!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
